                          Studer Award for outstanding contributions to Panhandle 
                          archeology from the Panhandle Archeological Society 
                          in 1999. On the right is Alvin Lynn, then the president 
                          of the PAS. Photo by Doug Boyd.</div></td>
                    </tr>
