                      <td height="554" valign="bottom"><a href="images/ac-corn.html" target="_blank"><img src="images/ac-corn-sm.jpg" alt="Photo of charred corn cobs, few of which are mroe than twice the size of a dime." width="200" height="227" class="thumbimg"></a> 
